        "id": 136,
        "name": "TAFE TRACTORS",
        "description": "<p><font color=\"#9c9c94\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">﻿</span><span style=\"font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">TAFE tractors are small commercial, low cost tractors ideal for farm, equestrian, agricultural and horticultural use. </span><span style=\"font-family: \"Open Sans\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18.4px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Their simple design means that minimal knowledge is required for operation and servicing. By avoiding sophisticated electronics and using interchangeable spare parts, the range</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 18.4px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">combines low cost, minimal maintenance with excellent durability. To view more models </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">available</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> to be ordered via us, press</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> </span></span></font></span><a href=\"https://www.tractorsuk.co.uk/small_commercial_tractor_models.php\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><u>here</u></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><u style=\"\">. </u>Please do not hesitate to give us a call for more information and pricing.</span></font></p>",
        "descriptionText": "TAFE tractors are small commercial, low cost tractors ideal for farm, equestrian, agricultural and horticultural use. Their simple design means that minimal knowledge is required for operation and servicing. By avoiding sophisticated electronics and using interchangeable spare parts, the range combines low cost, minimal maintenance with excellent durability. To view more models available to be ordered via us, press here . Please do not hesitate to give us a call for more information and pricing.",
